import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import '../App.css'

const HeaderComponent = () => {
    return (
        <Nav className="justify-content-center bg-dark " activeKey="/home">
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/home" id = "Hello" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 text-light ">Home</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/Projects" id = "Hello" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic text-light">Projects</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/Contact" id = "Hello" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic ">Contact</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/About" id = "Hello" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic ">
            About
          </Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
      </Nav>
    )
}

export default HeaderComponent
